                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d911">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 422.11G93/913</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Hartman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-02-17T17:00:00-05:14">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 17, 1917, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s February 13, 5 p.m. I presented note in person to the Minister for
                    Foreign Affairs this afternoon and fully complied with instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
